      "createdAt": "2025-04-15T07:57:29.318Z",
      "author": "Joshua07 (Joshua Johnson)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi All. I’d like to track the use of equipment at my wood shop but I’ve hit a snag. I only have one work van but have it listed on multiple boards so when I make a dashboard with to see where it will be on any day it has as many vans as I have it booked for. Is there a way to make the platform know it’s only one van no mater how many boards it’s listed on? See pic below. Thanks all.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/f/8f1348c369628532d364cca6143eda05e292d8de.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-04-14 102031\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/f/8f1348c369628532d364cca6143eda05e292d8de_2_690x246.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-04-14 102031\" width=\"690\" height=\"246\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-04-14 102031</span><span class=\"informations\">1409×504 35.7 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 227155,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2025-04-16T09:35:44.490Z",
      "author": "Megan345 (Megan)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi Joshua,</p>\n<p>I would tackle this like so:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Create a ‘Resources’ board where you list all your vans and any other critical tools that you need to schedule. You could also track e.g. MOT and service dates here, if that’s useful<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/7/573767377d3f125e6b93945107f1a40def832101.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/7/573767377d3f125e6b93945107f1a40def832101.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"413\" height=\"186\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">413×186 6.21 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>From the Resources board, create a Connect column (two-way) that links to all the boards where you want to schedule your van<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/b/1b85c80ded08e8cf9a2f02741d23b837b4368037.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/1/b/1b85c80ded08e8cf9a2f02741d23b837b4368037_2_690x299.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"299\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1123×488 35.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>In the individual scheduling boards, use the new Connect column that will have been created to schedule the van<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/5/259f0cbe6b9c4806bd9ff30f0f5165a5b4551337.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/5/259f0cbe6b9c4806bd9ff30f0f5165a5b4551337_2_690x236.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"236\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">968×332 23.1 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/1/b17088303b2e1c09e4018c680b5b850fc6eb215a.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/1/b17088303b2e1c09e4018c680b5b850fc6eb215a_2_690x213.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"213\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">880×272 19 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create a dashboard linked to your individual scheduling boards, and set the Resource Type to be the Link columns on each of the boards<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/3/f361b2f5ee608df70018032a8db5131ab763fa7f.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/f/3/f361b2f5ee608df70018032a8db5131ab763fa7f_2_690x347.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"347\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">845×425 30.4 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/2/8270f4cd338e7b54135ead48843eb668c7fd57ed.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/2/8270f4cd338e7b54135ead48843eb668c7fd57ed.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"377\" height=\"376\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">377×376 13.9 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The dashboard will then recognise your van as a single item rather than different lines<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/0/1014020e0b6073a665922774cc38a7442841dfe4.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/1/0/1014020e0b6073a665922774cc38a7442841dfe4_2_690x252.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"252\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">814×298 20.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n</ul>"
    },
